results.name: Fibonacci-like sequence of composite numbers with a(0) = 20615674205555510, a(1) = 3794765361567513.
comment: a(0) = 20615674205555510, a(1) = 3794765361567513. This is a second-order linear recurrence sequence with a(0) and a(1) coprime that does not contain any primes. It was found by Herbert S. Wilf in 1990.
